  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Youth promotion and contribution to disaster risk reduction in neighborhoods in South Lima</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Building on the experience and success of a previous project with Misereor, DESCO will promote youth participation in the management and reduction of risks in the face of climate change and potential disasters in three districts in southern Lima: Villa el Salvador, San Juan de Miraflores, and Villa Maria del Triunfo.  To this end, DESCO will empower young people to lead environmental urban management processes, helping them to improve the quality of life of people living in poverty and extreme poverty across these districts.</narrative>
  </description>
